Country: Orlando, Florida United States
Genre: Electronic
Style: Dark EBM, Gothic, Punk
Release Date: 14-11-2006
Quality: VBRkbps/44,1kHz/Joint-Stereo

BIO: Man and Machines has been an uprising force in the realm of underground industrial/electro/goth music in the last few years. Opening for such industrial acts as "Bile", "Hanzel and Gretyl", "Genitorturers", "Psyclon Nine", "Otto Von Schirach". "Razed in Black" and "Terrorfakt" Man and Machines is set on world exposure. With a pulsating, catchy and infectious EBM sound, Man and Machines is utter ear candy with a forceful punch in the face ! coming soon to your city. 

Ricki Gunz : All sequencing, beats and music arrangements. Production, Vocals, guitars, synths, samples and programming.
Angi Gunz : Vocals and Lyrics.
